page.title: 18PUBLIC TRANSPORT
page.content: There are two private coach operators working in this area. Carters is a Litcham firm and Freestones is based at White Mill, Green Lane, Beetley.Local schools use their services widely for transport to and from school, swimming lessons at Dereham and schools visits. On Wednesday a coach goes to Norwich and on Tuesday one goes to Kings Lynn.From Monday to Friday Freestones stop at Beetley turn five times a day at 0733,0833,1014,1259 and 1633. It then stops at The Swan Public House , Gressenhall 4 minutes later. It reaches its destination, Dereham Market Place 11 minutes later. On Saturday there are only three coaches running from Beetley and none from Gressenhall.
